name: Star-Clusters-Data-Analysis
description: Code used to fit star cluster data to the main sequence line as part of the UoB module Physics Laboratory 1 Astrolab.

name: horse_colic_data_with-_ML
description: This project aims to classify the condition of horses (whether they lived, died, or were euthanized) using various machine learning techniques. The raw data were obtained from the UCI Machine Learning Repository.

name: simple-ml.net-kmeans
description: A simple command line app written with ML.NET to cluster data from a CSV file.

name: Customer_Segmentation_Unsupervised_ML_Project
description: This repository contains code and documentation for an unsupervised machine learning project focused on customer segmentation. The project explores various clustering algorithms to group customers based on their behavior, preferences, and financial habits.

name: Wine_Quality_Analysis
description: This repository contains a script for performing exploratory data analysis (EDA) and clustering on red and white wine datasets. The goal is to combine data from both types of wines, visualize key features, and apply k-means clustering to uncover patterns and insights.

name: Parallelisation-Of-K-Means-Clustering
description: KMeans Parallelization implements KMeans clustering using MPI and subprocesses to optimize performance through parallel execution. This approach enhances scalability and efficiency, making it suitable for large datasets and high-performance computing environments.
